{"abstract": "In the book, she describes the ruthless ambition that affected the people close to her and tries to make amends for her years of boorish behavior.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/14/business/dealbook/in-memoir-erin-callan-steps-back-from-lehman-legacy.html", "snippet": "In the book, she describes the ruthless ambition that affected the people close to her and tries to make amends for her years of boorish behavior.", "lead_paragraph": "In May 2008, two months after Bear Stearns collapsed into the arms of JPMorgan Chase, sending paroxysms of fear from one end of Wall Street to the other, I had lunch with Erin Callan, who was then in her fifth month as the chief financial officer of Lehman Brothers. We met in one of the corporate dining rooms atop 745 Seventh Avenue, where the bank had moved in 2001 after its downtown Manhattan headquarters was rendered dysfunctional by the Sept. 11 attacks.", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2016/05/14/business/db-streetscene1/db-streetscene1-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 378, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2016/05/14/business/db-streetscene1/db-streetscene1-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 378}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2016/05/14/business/db-streetscene1/db-streetscene1-jumbo.jpg", "height": 644, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2016/05/14/business/db-streetscene1/db-streetscene1-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1289, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2016/05/14/b